snippet.title: Edgar - Bokbok In Boulzac (Release Trailer)
snippet.description:
Edgar - Bokbok in Boulzac is out now ! 

Crackpot outcast Edgar sets out to Boulzac to save his squash, and instead uncovers an unearthly secret at the heart of the city. A colourful, surreal and utterly bonkers point-and-click narrative adventure.

Learn more about it on https://www.edgar-boulzac.com
Follow Edgar on Twitter: https://twitter.com/edgarlpn
Chat with us on Discord: https://discord.gg/BVeKcrJ
